# IconButton

`TxIconButton` is a semantic `<button>` for compact icon actions. It exposes size, shape, pressed, disabled, native type, and a scoped slot for custom icon content.

Reviewed against `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/icon-button/src/TxIconButton.vue`.

## Basic Usage

### IconButton
