## Interaction Contract

- The root element is a real `button`; keyboard activation and disabled behavior are native.
- `label` becomes `aria-label`; provide it for icon-only controls.
- When `pressed` is boolean, the component emits `aria-pressed` and applies active styling.
- `disabled` blocks the native button and suppresses the component `click` emit.
- The default slot receives `{ hover, pressed }` for custom icon animations.

## API

### Props

| Prop | Type | Default | Description |
|------|------|---------|-------------|
| `icon` | `string` | `''` | Icon class/name rendered through `TxIcon` when no default slot is provided. |
| `label` | `string` | `''` | Accessible label. Required for icon-only actions. |
| `size` | `'sm' \| 'md' \| 'lg'` | `'md'` | Button size. |
| `shape` | `'square' \| 'circle' \| 'pill'` | `'square'` | Hit-area silhouette. |
| `pressed` | `boolean` | - | Toggle state; forwarded to `aria-pressed` when defined. |
| `disabled` | `boolean` | `false` | Native disabled state and visual disabled class. |
| `nativeType` | `'button' \| 'submit' \| 'reset'` | `'button'` | Native `type` attribute. |

### Events

| Event | Params | Description |
|------|--------|-------------|
| `click` | `(event: MouseEvent)` | Emitted for enabled clicks. |

### Slots

| Slot | Props | Description |
|------|------|-------------|
| `default` | `{ hover, pressed }` | Custom icon or animated content. |

## Best Practices

- Always set `label` unless visible text is supplied through the slot.
- Use `pressed` only for persistent toggles; use normal click buttons for one-shot actions.
- Keep destructive icon actions visually distinct through surrounding copy or confirmation, not icon color alone.
- Prefer `nativeType="button"` inside forms unless the button intentionally submits the form.

## Review Notes

- **Accessibility note:** `label` is the only built-in accessible name source for an icon-only button; if a custom slot includes visible text, verify it remains visible to assistive technologies.
- **Verified coverage:** No dedicated `icon-button` unit test exists yet; this page is source-reviewed against `TxIconButton.vue`, and `apps/nexus/test/docs/tuffex-component-docs-coverage.test.ts` verifies the component page plus demo registry remain loadable.

